MEntityLedgerPeriodCardView is a CardView
    show labels
    main column
        GeneralLedgerClosePeriod.GeneralLedgerCloseYear
            label is "Year"
        GeneralLedgerClosePeriod.PeriodName
            label is "Period"
        AccountingEntity
        Ledger
            select is WithoutCloseLedgerList
            raise red alert when (UnpostedJournals)
                mouse over text is "UnpostedJournalsExist"
        PeriodStatus
            label is "Status"
